			<tr>
				<td><font face="verdana" size="1">
				<img src="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/open.gif">&nbsp;<a href="/quests/default.asp">Quests</a><br>
				<img src="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tline.gif">
				<img src="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/open.gif">&nbsp;<a href="default.asp?land=1347">North Qeynos</a><br>
				<img src="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tline3.gif">
				<img src="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/open.gif">&nbsp;<b>Investigator Badge</b><br><br>
				</td>
			</tr>
				
			<tr>
			<td>
				<p>
					<font face="verdana" size="3"><b>    Investigator Badge</b>&nbsp;<a href="../Subscribe.asp?DID=459524"><font face="Verdana" size="2">[Subscribe to this document]</font></a></font>
					<br>
					<font face="verdana" size="2">
					<b><a href="mailto:">Ellesdee</a> | 
		                        6/28/2001 2:22:17 PM</b></font></p>
					
					<p>
					<font face="verdana" size="2">After the last patch a new npc called &quot;an investigator&quot; appeared in S.Qeynos, if you hail him nothing really happens.  He is connected to a human in full plate in the nqeynos guard house who claims to be leading an investigation into the bloodsabers.  tell him &quot;I am serious&quot; and he will send you on a quest to kill a corrupt guard named Shilster in North Karana.  Shilster is way off to the left of the wooden bridge if u are going to East Karana, approx lvl 22 I THINK.  Kill him and he drops a qeynos kite shield and his helm.  Take the helm and give it to the NPC in NQeynos who gave the quest.  He gives u a book and says u have to take a test to earn your badge.  Read the book and write down all the relevant parts, you'll see what I mean.  You take the book and give it to the investigator in SQeynos.  Ask the investigator &quot;who is the first suspect&quot;, then second, then third.  He will give u clues as to where to find the suspects as far as I know you MUST do it in order.  tell the investigator to &quot;follow me&quot; and he will follow u, don't let him out of your sight.  The first suspect is a guy in the Fireprides, walk up to him, hail him and say &quot;Are you a member of the Bloodsabers?&quot;  He will confess, ask the investigator &quot;I need a confession documant&quot; u get one give it to the bloodsaber and you get back a signed confession.  Here's the part I'm having problems with. The second suspect &quot;was last seen under the grounds of fate&quot;, the qeynos arena.... but I can't find him, neither of the steel warriors usually at the basement are bloodsabers.  The third suspect is near Raz the Rat Misk, u can fund him at the docks easily.  I don't know what the award for this quest is, hope someone can find out where the second suspect is.            Ellesdee Toxavenger, level 27 paladin Druzzil Ro<BR>

			<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</font></p>
					</p>
			</td>
			</tr>
