				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				The msg about writhing in the grip of agony is Shilster's Harmtouch - he's a shadowknight.  This quest is pretty easy for anyone lvl 25 and above, and has quite the story behind it too.  <BR>
The first guy in in Fireprides, the second is under the arena in the room with all the doors.  He stands by the big hook that hangs from the ceiling near the pillory &lt;the wood thing sticking up from the floor&gt;  He'll deny being a Bloodsaber but give him a confession document anyway and he caves and signs it.  The third guy is by the Rat Misk and he will fight you - so be prepared.  He's an SK too.  Just make sure he doesn't kill the investigator or its a long wait for him to respawn.  Turn in the two confessions plus the third guy's head and voila - you have your badge.  The investigator gave me a key phrase to tell Vegalys but he says that there is no further service he needs from me at this time &lt;or words to that effect&gt;  I'm going to try back after the next patch to see if the quest continues.  Here's hoping its a multi-stage one like the ring and shawl in Velious =)<BR>
